Add a Group in GoPhish
✅ Step 1: Go to “Users & Groups”
Log in to GoPhish at:
https://127.0.0.1:3333

On the left-hand menu, click “Users & Groups”.

Click the green “+ New Group” button.

✅ Step 2: Enter Group Details
Group Name:
Enter something like:
Test Users or Phishing Simulation Group

✅ Step 3: Add Users to the Group
You have two options:

🔹 Option 1: Manually Add Users One by One
Click “+ Add Recipient”.

Enter the following fields:

First Name

Last Name

Email

Position (optional)

Repeat for each user.

✅ Step 4: Save the Group
After adding users, click the green “Save Group” button.
